</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-131_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong>Learning</strong></h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-133_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-134_ pf-text-1"><strong>Absorbing new ideas</strong> - These teams learn and integrate new ideas into their innovation processes.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-136_ pf-text-1"><strong>Continuous improvement</strong> - They are committed to continuous learning and improving their methods and strategies.
